## 1. Project Overview

This is a university academic portal with three types of users:

| User | What they do |
|---|---|
| **Student** | Register for courses, pay fees, view results, view transcript |
| **Admin** | Manage faculties, departments, courses, approve registrations, publish results |
| **Lecturer** | View assigned courses, view their students, upload results |

The backend is fully built and deployed. Your job is to build the React frontend that connects to it.

