## 5. Response Format

**Every single endpoint** returns the same shape:

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Human readable message",
  "data": { ... }
}
```

So always access your data like this:
```javascript
const response = await api.get("/students");
const students = response.data.data; // ← always .data.data
```

For errors:
```json
{
  "success": false,
  "message": "Error description"
}
```

